  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a not-so-distant future, the technology that promised to connect humanity ended up isolating it. Life became too practical, too complex, too gray.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/739433b7e2b41a4bc1f66274daaf763b.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/739433b7e2b41a4bc1f66274daaf763b.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span>That was when they said: \"Relive your best memories.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/9f052c4455a5b0bc5f51aeb73ca6ef00.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/9f052c4455a5b0bc5f51aeb73ca6ef00.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memories became the key to understanding life. Humans, desperate for emotion, sought to heal their traumas or feel alive once again. Most chose to live in lucid dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/b2ccacf3db2dff1f561d4e06cd338a80.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/b2ccacf3db2dff1f561d4e06cd338a80.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span>You, the player, are the most advanced Artificial Intelligence ever created. Your mission? Explore and understand human life through a crucial memory. Discover possibilities and learn what it means to live.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/a1ccb6908781d95454904b1415232637.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/a1ccb6908781d95454904b1415232637.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a detailed interactive memory that presents an emotional and engaging story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make decisions at key moments, shaping the outcome of the memory based on your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an intuitive interface with dialogue options and navigation that put you in control of the narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience multiple possible endings, determined by the choices you make throughout the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize features like quick save and load, allowing you to revisit previous decisions to explore different paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock achievements by exploring various outcomes and understanding the nuances of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden secrets and narrative branches by delving deep into choices and interactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/c9800275342b3049b5277a0e0a7fdf5f.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/c9800275342b3049b5277a0e0a7fdf5f.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a not-so-distant future, the technology that promised to connect humanity ended up isolating it. Life became too practical, too complex, too gray.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/739433b7e2b41a4bc1f66274daaf763b.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/739433b7e2b41a4bc1f66274daaf763b.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span>That was when they said: \"Relive your best memories.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/9f052c4455a5b0bc5f51aeb73ca6ef00.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/9f052c4455a5b0bc5f51aeb73ca6ef00.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memories became the key to understanding life. Humans, desperate for emotion, sought to heal their traumas or feel alive once again. Most chose to live in lucid dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras/b2ccacf3db2dff1f561d4e06cd338a80.avif?t=1754636715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408820/extras_big/b2ccacf3db2dff1f561d4e06cd338a80.avif?t=1754636715 width=800 height=304 /></span>You, the player, are the most advanced Artificial Intelligence ever created. Your mission? Explore and understand human life through a crucial memory. Discover possibilities and learn what it means to live.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset